7. TERMINATION & CURE
   Your rights under this license terminate automatically if you breach
   any term. However, if you cease all violation within 30 days of
   discovery, your rights are reinstated retroactively. Reinstatement
   is automatic if the copyright holder notifies you of the violation
   and you cure within 30 days. If you violate this license a second
   time, your rights terminate permanently.

8. AUDIT
   The copyright holder may request, no more than once per year, that
   you provide reasonable proof of compliance with this license,
   including documentation of revenue (if applicable) and charitable
   payments made. You must respond within 60 days.

9. NO WARRANTY
