DEFINITIONS:
- "Commercial use" means use by any entity primarily for commercial
  advantage or monetary compensation
- "Software" means all files in this repository
- "Gross revenue" means total revenue before expenses, taxes, and costs
- "Attributable revenue" means revenue directly generated by or enabled
  through the use of this Software, including but not limited to products,
  services, or features that incorporate or depend on this Software
- "Market sector" means the company's primary industry as defined
  by standard classification systems (e.g., NAICS, SIC, GICS)
- "Average revenue for their market sector" means the median gross
  revenue for companies in the same sector, published by
  recognized industry data sources
- "Publicly voted" means decided by open ballot with at least 30 days
  notice and 7-day voting period on the primary public repository
